{"tid":782332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】ICAC拘捕至少兩警涉收賄包庇夜場 不排除有更多警員被捕","createTime":"2018-08-16T15:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T14:59:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":160,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5d90cc9b31b8cc89e65d313e7ec3033e98804e","tid":782332,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"再有警務人員涉收賄包庇夜場被捕。消息稱，廉政公署早前接獲線報，指多個警區疑有警務人員涉嫌接受利益，向區內的娛樂場所負責人通風報信，披露警方調查的機密資料，並向他們提供意見或協助。據了解，深水埗警區一名軍裝警員及旺角警區一名刑事調查隊探員被廉署人員帶走調查。<br />\n<br />\n廉署相信有更多警務人員涉案，正展開進一步調查，不排除有更多人被捕。廉署發言人回覆查詢時表示，根據政策，廉署一般不會評論個別事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180816/bkn-20180816230628579-0816_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180816%2Fbkn-20180816230628579-0816_00822_001.html&d=vXIrtQr4zSkx1uc2bfDxFzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=76cf4d10\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180816/bkn-20180816230628579-0816_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a54b9611144ddbed45f7a344129649e0f4aa5dfe","tid":782332,"uid":2718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8ebc6bed4d7a65ebee9b5336a9e0ffbcdbb8b9","tid":782332,"uid":162303,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:46:54.000Z","msg":"真正警黑大合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae34ca0a6754708cd5d8eff9c2af12492c31588","tid":782332,"uid":13492,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:47:21.000Z","msg":"阿Sir收片唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d164fd3321933473f43a84faf596ded40016389d","tid":782332,"uid":37808,"like":35